    "c_foundation_health_mK3Tz9": {
      "type": "c-foundation-health",
      "blocks": {
        "benefit_tab_UpixnV": {
          "type": "benefit_tab",
          "settings": {
            "open_by_default": false,
            "title": "Cardiovascular Health",
            "description": "Supports healthy blood pressure, blood flow, and arterial flexibility",
            "ingredient_1": "Potassium Nitrate",
            "ingredient_2": "Vitamin C",
            "ingredient_3": "Magnesium",
            "ingredient_4": "Fermented Beet Root",
            "ingredient_5": "Beetroot Extract (25% Betaine Nitrate)",
            "details": "<p>Berkeley Life works via the dietary nitrate to nitrite to Nitric Oxide pathway, validated in double-blind, placebo-controlled trials. Nitric Oxide signals blood vessels to relax and widen, improving blood flow and supporting healthy blood pressure. Clinical research on Berkeley Life's formula showed reductions in carotid artery stiffness and improvements in vascular responsiveness after 8 to 12 weeks of daily use. Magnesium reinforces this by further relaxing smooth muscle in blood vessel walls. For anyone searching for the best Nitric Oxide supplements for cardiovascular support, this clinically tested formula sets a clear standard.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab_energy": {
          "type": "benefit_tab",
          "settings": {
            "open_by_default": false,
            "title": "Energy & Endurance",
            "description": "Boosts oxygen delivery to muscles for lasting stamina and faster recovery",
            "ingredient_1": "Potassium Nitrate",
            "ingredient_2": "Vitamin C",
            "ingredient_3": "Magnesium",
            "ingredient_4": "Fermented Beet Root",
            "ingredient_5": "Beetroot Extract (25% Betaine Nitrate)",
            "details": "<p>Nitric Oxide improves how efficiently your muscles receive and use oxygen. Berkeley Life's clinical trial subjects showed a 300% increase in capacity to produce energy after 3 months. Vitamin B12 and Thiamin (B1) are essential cofactors in cellular energy metabolism, and Magnesium plays a direct role in ATP production. The result is sustained stamina and reduced fatigue, with no stimulants. This is what separates a clinically backed Nitric Oxide supplement from a standard multivitamin.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab_cognitive": {
          "type": "benefit_tab",
          "settings": {
            "open_by_default": false,
            "title": "Cognitive Function",
            "description": "Promotes cerebral blood flow for mental clarity, focus and mood",
            "ingredient_1": "Potassium Nitrate",
            "ingredient_2": "Vitamin C",
            "ingredient_3": "Magnesium",
            "ingredient_4": "Fermented Beet Root",
            "ingredient_5": "Beetroot Extract (25% Betaine Nitrate)",
            "details": "<p>The brain consumes roughly 20% of the body's blood supply. By driving vasodilation via the nitrate-to-NO pathway, Berkeley Life supports the cerebral blood flow needed for sharp thinking and sustained focus. Vitamin B12 is critical for neurological function, nerve sheath integrity, and neurotransmitter synthesis. Thiamin (B1) supports glucose metabolism in the brain, the primary fuel for cognitive performance. Supporting Nitric Oxide blood flow to the brain is one of the most effective ways to support mental clarity as you age.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab_sexual": {
          "type": "benefit_tab",
          "settings": {
            "open_by_default": false,
            "title": "Sexual Health",
            "description": "Supports libido, arousal and performance for men and women",
            "ingredient_1": "Potassium Nitrate",
            "ingredient_2": "Vitamin C",
            "ingredient_3": "Magnesium",
            "ingredient_4": "Fermented Beet Root",
            "ingredient_5": "Beetroot Extract (25% Betaine Nitrate)",
            "details": "<p>Nitric Oxide is the key molecule behind blood flow to every part of the body, including sexual function. Berkeley Life's clinical pilot showed a 75% increase in libido and 83% enhanced orgasm after 60 days. Improved blood flow supports desire and performance in both men and women. Vitamin C enhances NO bioavailability by reducing oxidative breakdown, extending the duration and magnitude of each dose. That is why Nitric Oxide pills focused on vascular health can also have a meaningful impact on sexual wellness.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab_blood_flow": {
          "type": "benefit_tab",
          "settings": {
            "open_by_default": false,
            "title": "ACTIVE AGING",
            "description": "Counteracts the age-related NO decline that drives cardiovascular and metabolic risk",
            "ingredient_1": "Potassium Nitrate",
            "ingredient_2": "Vitamin C",
            "ingredient_3": "Magnesium",
            "ingredient_4": "Fermented Beet Root",
            "ingredient_5": "Beetroot Extract (25% Betaine Nitrate)",
            "details": "<p>After age 40, the body's ability to produce Nitric Oxide declines significantly, reducing blood flow and increasing cardiovascular strain. Berkeley Life's Nitric Oxide Support helps replenish NO levels through the dietary nitrate pathway, supporting vascular flexibility, healthy blood pressure, and metabolic efficiency. Among the top Nitric Oxide supplements available today, Berkeley Life is one of the few backed by double-blind, placebo-controlled clinical trials. Vitamin C enhances NO bioavailability by reducing oxidative breakdown, extending the duration and magnitude of each dose.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
